feel nothing

1291
02:00:24,092 --> 02:00:25,760
so as not to feel anything.

1292
02:00:27,846 --> 02:00:28,930
What a waste.

1293
02:00:37,022 --> 02:00:38,356
Have I spoken out of turn?

1294
02:00:43,195 --> 02:00:44,779
And I'll say one more thing,

1295
02:00:48,533 --> 02:00:49,743
it'll clear the air.

1296
02:00:52,746 --> 02:00:54,164
I may have come close

1297
02:00:55,707 --> 02:00:57,417
but I never had
what you two have.

1298
02:01:00,212 --> 02:01:03,715
Something always held me back

1299
02:01:04,799 --> 02:01:06,634
or stood in the way.

1300
02:01:11,639 --> 02:01:13,975
How you live your life
is your business.

1301
02:01:14,017 --> 02:01:16,561
Just remember,

1302
02:01:18,646 --> 02:01:21,900
our hearts and our bodies
are given to us only once,

1303
02:01:25,028 --> 02:01:27,864
and before you know it,
your heart's worn out.

1304
02:01:28,615 --> 02:01:31,243
And as for your body,

1305
02:01:31,283 --> 02:01:33,411
there comes a point
when no one looks at it

1306
02:01:35,038 --> 02:01:36,706
much less wants
to come near it.

1307
02:01:40,210 --> 02:01:46,507
Right now,
there's sorrow, pain.

1308
02:01:47,050 --> 02:01:48,384
Don't kill it,

1309
02:01:50,053 --> 02:01:52,722
and with it,
the joy you felt.

1310
02:02:04,818 --> 02:02:06,194
